    "name": "Unfair Rampage: Knightfall",
    "steam_appid": 3187470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go back in time with a big gun and shiny armor and dominate! It’s <strong>FAST,</strong> and you are in <strong>FULL CONTROL</strong> in this 2.5D platformer. Before you know it, you’ll be <i>in the zone</i>, dashing, double-jumping, and ploughing through enemies while dodging hazards and racking up a high score!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/9018b94370147c70c2f1085923da40d5.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/9018b94370147c70c2f1085923da40d5.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/9018b94370147c70c2f1085923da40d5.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SUPER TIGHT</strong> controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ULTRA FAST</strong> action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESTRUCTIBLE</strong> levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER</strong> up to 4 local players (+ Steam Remote Play)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROCEDURAL </strong>worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLOCKABLE</strong> skins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STATS</strong> (tons of them!) &amp; leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RETRO</strong>-inspired soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHALLENGING</strong> cinematic camera option</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REPLAYABILITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world changes with every game you play, keeping each game nice and fresh, but you will recognise patterns and learn to conquer them! Use POWERUPS to boost your weapon and shield yourself from harm's way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/a2bc0b321d2a434a33be4e29ee5613d6.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/a2bc0b321d2a434a33be4e29ee5613d6.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/a2bc0b321d2a434a33be4e29ee5613d6.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REWARDING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is HARD, especially at first. You’ll die a lot, but restarting the game is super quick, and you’ll get a little further each time. Before you know it, you'll feel rewarded as you cross the first bridge regaining full health, and you’re on your way to meet the big evil knight boss for an epic fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f26a57ed79f29c490537e4f217c1913e.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f26a57ed79f29c490537e4f217c1913e.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f26a57ed79f29c490537e4f217c1913e.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHOWING OFF</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get up close, and your attack will turn you into a martial artist, kicking your opponents all over the place. At this point, you can start showing off =)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/067a410b7af3cc4d26d97c952b4ccd9c.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/067a410b7af3cc4d26d97c952b4ccd9c.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/067a410b7af3cc4d26d97c952b4ccd9c.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CINEMATIC CAMERA OPTION</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game in a challenging cinematic camera mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/25d8ffe1b9f2481a99a349c4c072280e.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/25d8ffe1b9f2481a99a349c4c072280e.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/25d8ffe1b9f2481a99a349c4c072280e.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LOCAL MULTIPLAYER &amp; STEAM REMOTE PLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play up to 4 players locally or remotely through Steam Remote Play. You play co-op to beat the level. If any player is eliminated, they respawn when another player reaches the bridge and you can compete against eachother by trying to get the higher score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f57cb7a817987847fb0acdee5331b874.poster.avif?t=1761293701\" width=610 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f57cb7a817987847fb0acdee5331b874.webm?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187470/extras/f57cb7a817987847fb0acdee5331b874.mp4?t=1761293701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HELLO FROM IMPHENZIA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! I’m a solo developer who loves designing games, programming, creating art, animating characters, composing music, and making sound effects. I want to make fun games in my low-poly style. If you grew up in the 80s and 90s - like me - I want to make games “<strong><i>the way you remember them</i></strong>”—not how they <i>actually</i> were (slower with sparse visuals). </p>",
